quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  40,67,"Huwa allathee khalaqakum min turabinthumma min nutfatin thumma min AAalaqatin thummayukhrijukum tiflan thumma litablughoo ashuddakum thummalitakoonoo shuyookhan waminkum man yutawaffa min qabluwalitablughoo ajalan musamman walaAAallakum taAAqiloon"
  40,68,"Huwa allathee yuhyee wayumeetufa-itha qada amran fa-innama yaqoolu lahukun fayakoon"
  40,69,"Alam tara ila allatheena yujadiloonafee ayati Allahi anna yusrafoon"
  40,70,"Allatheena kaththaboo bilkitabiwabima arsalna bihi rusulana fasawfayaAAlamoon"
  40,71,"Ithi al-aghlalu fee aAAnaqihimwassalasilu yushaboon"
  40,72,"Fee alhameemi thumma fee annariyusjaroon"
  40,73,"Thumma qeela lahum ayna ma kuntumtushrikoon"
  40,74,"Min dooni Allahi qaloo dallooAAanna bal lam nakun nadAAoo min qablu shay-an kathalikayudillu Allahu alkafireen"
  40,75,"Thalikum bima kuntum tafrahoonafee al-ardi bighayri alhaqqi wabima kuntumtamrahoon"
  40,76,"Odkhuloo abwaba jahannama khalideenafeeha fabi/sa mathwa almutakabbireen"
  40,77,"Fasbir inna waAAda Allahihaqqun fa-imma nuriyannaka baAAda allatheenaAAiduhum aw natawaffayannaka fa-ilayna yurjaAAoon"
